attributes.title: Play Pals Super Bunny Man Funny Moments
attributes.caption: Now, for the first time ever, watch the entire series’ highs and lows in the time it takes for a single lunch break. Hop to it, summer bois!
attributes.description: History changed when Michael Jones and Gavin Free picked up their controllers and assumed bunny form that fateful day in 2018. 9 hours of gameplay later, the world was rocked to its core and possibly the stupidest content ever was set loose on the internet. Since then there have been many imitators *ahem* Game Grumps Markiplier sir edd *AHEM* but only one true let’s play. Now, for the first time ever, watch the entire series’ highs and lows in the time it takes for a single lunch break. Hop to it, summer bois!
attributes.display_title: Play Pals Super Bunny Man Funny Moments

attributes.title: We tried an Elden Ring Randomizer with CO-OP and became ELDEN BROS!
attributes.caption: While we’re waiting for Elden Ring DLC to be announced, Michael and Alfredo started a new playthrough with a mod that allows them to co-op seamlessly in Elden Ring.
attributes.description:
While we’re waiting for Elden Ring DLC to be announced, Michael and Alfredo started a new playthrough with a mod that allows them to co-op seamlessly in Elden Ring. Plus, there’s a randomizer that changes up all the items and enemies in the game, even bosses. As the Elden Bros battle their way through Limgrave and Stormveil Castle, they encounter some truly broken nonsense. Do you want to see them take on Liurnia in this co-op randomizer? |
Cut together from:
Elden Ring Randomizer Hurts | Let's Play Co-op
Elden Ring Randomizer #2 | Was Godrick Replaced By A Giant Lava Snake?
attributes.display_title: We tried an Elden Ring Randomizer with CO-OP and became ELDEN BROS!

attributes.title: Best of Achievement Hunter September 2022
attributes.caption: From playing Uno for over 37 hours, impersonating a Kryptonian in Gmod, and voting on the Xbox 360 being the best video game console of all time in console wars, it has been an amazing month!
attributes.description:
This month has come and passed
Together we gamed and laughed
Wake me up when September ends

From playing Uno for over 37 hours, impersonating a Kryptonian in Gmod, and voting on the Xbox 360 being the best video game console of all time in console wars, it has been an amazing month! Between Halo 5, The Legend of Zelda, Dark Souls, and all of the other games we played, which has been your favorite to watch?

attributes.title: Best of Achievement Hunter October 2022
attributes.caption: It’s the spookiest season of all, meaning a lot of jump scares in VR, twisted variations on classic formats, and extreme difficulty. Out of Halo 5 LASO, a 7 Days to Die run with permadeath, and Joe playing his first Souls game, which do you think is the greater challenge?

attributes.title: Uno Infinite in 224 Minutes
attributes.caption: Do you want to see the descent into madness Achievement Hunter experienced when playing Uno for over 37 hours straight, but you don't have over 37 hours to spare?
attributes.description: Do you want to see the descent into madness Achievement Hunter experienced when playing Uno for over 37 hours straight, but you don't have over 37 hours to spare? Well then you're in luck!! For the low, low price of 3 hours and 44 minutes, you too can get the Uno Infinite experience delivered directly to your eyeballs. Will you see every single Uno card we had to play? Absolutely definitely not. Will you get enough Uno Infinite highlights to fill out a full evening of entertainment? Absolutely.

attributes.title: Best of Achievement Hunter November 2022
attributes.caption: November is a great time to say thanks! From God of War: Ragnarök to 7 Days to Die, breaking in the brand new office to Extra Life, we've got so much to be thankful for. What are some moments from Achievement Hunter that you're grateful for this year?
